1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:45,820
=Episode 30=

16
00:01:47,959 --> 00:01:49,879
(CEO Jiang Dongchao Dismissal Notice)
This is your dismissal notice.

17
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,400
It carries

18
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:53,359
the signatures of all the board members.

19
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:19,879
Jiang Dongchao.

20
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:30,719
I can finally

21
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:32,240
leave you for good.

22
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:36,090
Don't even think about using
our daughter to control me again.

23
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:41,280
My lawyer will represent me

24
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,900
in filing a divorce lawsuit against you.

25
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:44,560
As for the evidence

26
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:46,639
of all the violence
you've inflicted on me,

27
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:49,080
I've already submitted it all.

28
00:02:50,190 --> 00:02:51,479
You didn't expect this, did you?

29
00:02:52,479 --> 00:02:54,000
I was the one who gave

30
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:56,599
the evidence of your crimes to Rao Yuci.

31
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,599
This is not

32
00:02:58,599 --> 00:02:59,719
an ordinary necklace.

33
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,560
I hope it helps you all.

34
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,639
Please.

35
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,080
Thank you.

36
00:03:29,039 --> 00:03:29,840
But

37
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,879
are you sure about giving it to me?

38
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,080
To be precise,

39
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:38,400
I should be the one thanking you.

40
00:03:40,199 --> 00:03:41,719
You gave me hope.

41
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,520
You gave my daughter

42
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:54,199
a safe future.

43
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:05,520
Let's go.

44
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,519
I came from Wall Street.

45
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:23,100
Have I ever lost in the past ten years?

46
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:26,160
We'll make Wall Street tremble

47
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,240
for all of us,

48
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,240
the Chinese!

49
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:34,720
Has such a vibrant national enterprise

50
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,240
just lost its spirit like this?

51
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:37,959
David,

52
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:40,519
if I remember correctly,

53
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,600
you just celebrated
your 35th birthday last month.

54
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,160
Your child

55
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:46,319
just started second grade, right?

56
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,839
Your monthly mortgage, car loan,

57
00:04:49,439 --> 00:04:50,759
and international school fees

58
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,439
are quite

59
00:04:51,439 --> 00:04:52,759
a significant amount altogether.

60
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:55,120
And your wife was just laid off.

61
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,120
Steven, I heard that your mother

62
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,100
has been in the hospital

63
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,439
for almost a year due to a stroke.

64
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:05,399
How much are the medical expenses

65
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,480
for this year?

66
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,199
Isn't their situation

67
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,680
the same as yours?

68
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,680
By coming to Lysen,

69
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,519
you gained more than just
a respectable job

70
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:17,560
and a high salary.

71
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,759
It carries the expectations
of your parents,

72
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,720
wives, husbands,

73
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:24,839
and children.

74
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,160
And all of this

75
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,240
could likely

76
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,279
vanish today!

77
00:05:29,319 --> 00:05:30,199
We're doing this

78
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:32,160
as a commitment

79
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:34,439
to our hometown and to every investor.

80
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,720
Lysen

81
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:38,040
will always stand
on the side of justice,

82
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:39,560
protecting every penny

83
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,079
of our investors' hard-earned money.

84
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:44,240
Because I am the person

85
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:46,199
responsible for all strategic decisions

86
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,160
at Lysen.

87
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:52,540
♪I'm coming back enraged♪

88
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:58,380
♪Bring the fire to the game
and paint it red♪

89
00:05:58,380 --> 00:06:00,580
♪With blood♪

90
00:06:00,580 --> 00:06:04,100
♪From the start to the end
you're damned♪

91
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:08,380
♪I'm coming back untamed♪

92
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:09,879
Move. Get in the car.

93
00:06:09,879 --> 00:06:16,060
♪And I'm standing on
the traumatized ruins unbent♪

94
00:06:16,860 --> 00:06:20,900
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

95
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:22,759
All of your crimes

96
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:24,040
will be punished.

97
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,240
Your past sins

98
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,480
will be revealed one by one.

99
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:30,399
The best retribution

100
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:31,519
for a villain like you

101
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:32,839
is to fall

102
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:34,279
just when you

103
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:37,160
are closest to success.

104
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,600
Jiang Dongchao,

105
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:46,759
didn't you say

106
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:48,220
there are no miracles for good people?

107
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,680
A miracle has happened.

108
00:06:57,300 --> 00:07:01,100
(Defendant Jiang Dongchao is sentenced
to life imprisonment for fund-raising fraud,)

109
00:07:01,101 --> 00:07:04,900
(deprived of political rights for life,
and his personal property is confiscated.)

110
00:07:07,780 --> 00:07:11,788
(Defendant Bai Qingyu, for instigating
Bai Liangliang to commit intentional injury,)

111
00:07:11,789 --> 00:07:15,100
(is sentenced to six months in prison
for the crime of attempted intentional injury.)

112
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:19,205
(Han Congfei's unauthorized filming
and spreading of false information)

113
00:07:19,206 --> 00:07:20,708
(have infringed
on others' reputation rights.)

114
00:07:20,709 --> 00:07:23,714
(Given that the victim decided not to pursue charges,
Han Congfei has issued a public apology.)

115
00:07:23,715 --> 00:07:26,420
(The account posting the false info
has been permanently banned.)

116
00:07:31,580 --> 00:07:33,445
(Miss Gao's illegal bug
installation violated)

117
00:07:33,446 --> 00:07:35,560
(the Public Security Administration
Punishment Law.)

118
00:07:35,561 --> 00:07:37,650
(According to Article 42 of the Public Security
Administration Punishment Law,)

119
00:07:37,651 --> 00:07:39,740
(it is decided to impose an administrative
detention of five days on Miss Gao.)

120
00:07:41,460 --> 00:07:42,532
(After Bai Muran committed suicide
to avoid punishment,)

121
00:07:42,533 --> 00:07:43,956
(the public security organ, based on
the scene investigation and evidence,)

122
00:07:43,957 --> 00:07:45,828
(and the forensic appraisal,
decided not to file)

123
00:07:45,829 --> 00:07:47,700
(a case according
to the Criminal Procedure Law.)

124
00:07:53,180 --> 00:07:57,090
(Chen Mo's medical license was revoked
for violating the Law on Medical Practitioners.)

125
00:07:57,100 --> 00:08:00,060
(He is prohibited from engaging
in medical-related work for five years.)

126
00:08:07,860 --> 00:08:11,540
(Xinkang Treatment Center)

127
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,079
Checkmate!

128
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,160
Come on, stop that.

129
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:34,279
Have you really decided
not to return to Lysen?

130
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:37,360
Yeah.

131
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:41,440
It feels like a lifetime ago.

132
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,360
Do you remember

133
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,240
that time you came to see us?

134
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:46,519
You still wanted

135
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:48,159
to achieve your little dream at Lysen.

136
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:50,600
(Reception Room)

137
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:52,290
Instead of going on
a date on the weekend,

138
00:08:52,519 --> 00:08:53,320
you came to see

139
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,679
us "young hunks".

140
00:08:54,879 --> 00:08:56,279
You really don't know how to talk.

141
00:08:56,279 --> 00:08:57,240
Weren't you always

142
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,679
muttering about "young girls"?

143
00:08:58,679 --> 00:08:59,559
Get lost.

144
00:08:59,559 --> 00:09:00,559
Keep your mouth shut.

145
00:09:00,799 --> 00:09:01,600
Fine.

146
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,540
Since the "young hunks" are always
muttering about "young girls",

147
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:08,110
then the "young girl" has to come visit
the "young hunks," right?

148
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:10,399
I'll come see you

149
00:09:10,399 --> 00:09:11,440
every weekend.

150
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:12,840
You're the smartest.

151
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:15,399
By the way, how's the plan going?

152
00:09:15,399 --> 00:09:16,200
Is it smooth?

153
00:09:17,399 --> 00:09:19,519
Anyway, everyone in Dept 3 knows.

154
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:21,000
Now, everyone at Lysen

155
00:09:21,039 --> 00:09:22,039
knows that I gave up

156
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:23,200
a major project to work

157
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:25,200
on the Linwei Alley
Snack Street Renewal.

158
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,960
Are those people in Dept 3 reliable?

159
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:30,790
It would be great
if we could work together.

160
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:31,919
But if we can't,

161
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,799
I'll be fine on my own.

162
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:36,639
The world outside

163
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:39,039
sounds much more interesting than here.

164
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:40,879
The people here

165
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:44,240
are much more
clear-headed than those outside.

166
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,559
You can always come back.

167
00:09:47,559 --> 00:09:48,559
She finally made it out,

168
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:49,919
so why would she come back?

169
00:09:50,159 --> 00:09:50,879
Is it appropriate

170
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:53,200
for her to be with crazy people like us?

171
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,559
I'm not crazy.

172
00:09:54,559 --> 00:09:55,759
You're not crazy,

173
00:09:55,759 --> 00:09:56,840
you're just nuts.

174
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,440
I'm warning you guys!

175
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,120
I...

176
00:10:00,159 --> 00:10:01,000
I'll shut up.

177
00:10:03,639 --> 00:10:04,440
Yuci,

178
00:10:05,750 --> 00:10:07,120
you're surrounded by backstabbers,

179
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,559
so be careful.

180
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:11,159
Bai Liangliang will find ways

181
00:10:11,159 --> 00:10:12,159
to hurt you.

182
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,519
Don't worry, Young Hunk.

183
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:19,879
Lately,

184
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,559
I often think back

185
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:25,240
to how you were when you first arrived.

186
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,399
I still remember

187
00:10:27,399 --> 00:10:28,320
you told me

188
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:31,639
that Master was a bad old man.

189
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:35,200
He had too many crooked ideas.

190
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:36,919
That's why he went bald.

191
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:40,320
Those were all his flaws.

192
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,720
But he actually had many virtues.

193
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,600
We all miss him very much.

194
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,679
He had terrible table manners,

195
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,559
just like a pig.

196
00:10:48,559 --> 00:10:49,200
Right!

197
00:10:50,500 --> 00:10:52,500
He never closed the door
when using the toilet,

198
00:10:52,559 --> 00:10:54,159
and it stank so much.

199
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:55,320
I smelled it often.

200
00:10:55,639 --> 00:10:56,440
Who was it?

201
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:58,360
Who else? We're talking about you!

202
00:10:58,759 --> 00:10:59,559
Who was it?

203
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:02,639
Who...

204
00:11:03,559 --> 00:11:04,360
It's me,

205
00:11:05,159 --> 00:11:05,960
Yuci.

206
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,200
You're awake?

207
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,559
Who's talking behind my back?

208
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:12,360
No one.

209
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:14,879
They were praising you.

210
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:15,799
Nonsense.

211
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,279
Don't believe them.

212
00:11:20,279 --> 00:11:21,639
You're finally awake.

213
00:11:21,639 --> 00:11:22,799
I was so worried...

214
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,240
I just stepped out for a bit,

215
00:11:26,879 --> 00:11:28,279
and I rushed back.

216
00:11:30,519 --> 00:11:31,679
I missed you.

217
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,720
I missed you, too.

218
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,720
You're finally awake.

219
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:45,879
Don't cry.

220
00:12:29,900 --> 00:12:31,039
Take a photo as a memento.

221
00:12:31,039 --> 00:12:32,679
Look at how much she wants to take one.

222
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:01,080
(This is the letter)

223
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,080
(Mr. Chen left for you.)

224
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:04,720
(He said he wants you to be happy)

225
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:08,759
(because you have a beautiful smile.)

226
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,360
(Thank you.)

227
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,399
(Yuci,)

228
00:13:25,410 --> 00:13:26,799
(by the time you see this letter,)

229
00:13:26,799 --> 00:13:27,879
(I will have already left.)

230
00:13:29,039 --> 00:13:29,960
(You were right.)

231
00:13:31,679 --> 00:13:32,440
(In your story,)

232
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,840
(no one is innocent,)

233
00:13:34,799 --> 00:13:35,840
(including me.)

234
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:38,919
(I once thought)

235
00:13:40,159 --> 00:13:41,399
(I could heal myself)

236
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,879
(by burying everything from the past,)

237
00:13:45,399 --> 00:13:47,279
(making it all disappear
without a trace.)

238
00:13:48,799 --> 00:13:50,039
(But I never imagined)

239
00:13:50,039 --> 00:13:51,440
(that the backlash of fate)

240
00:13:52,879 --> 00:13:55,120
(would cause our two)

241
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,639
(different trajectories to overlap,)

242
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,559
(making me fall in love with you.)

243
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,440
(Did I ever tell you?)

244
00:14:04,519 --> 00:14:06,159
(I love seeing your different sides.)

245
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:07,840
(You're beautiful no matter what.)

246
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,600
Yuci.

247
00:14:11,399 --> 00:14:13,039
Where you're standing now

248
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:16,639
is where you hit me before.

249
00:14:19,300 --> 00:14:20,700
(You look beautiful when you smile.)

250
00:14:21,799 --> 00:14:23,880
(You look beautiful
when you're frowning and angry.)

251
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:26,000
(You look beautiful
when expressionless.)

252
00:14:26,639 --> 00:14:27,519
(And even)

253
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,500
(when you're being reckless,)

254
00:14:29,919 --> 00:14:30,960
(cold-blooded,)

255
00:14:31,919 --> 00:14:34,100
(and focused on your goals,
you still look beautiful.)

256
00:14:35,759 --> 00:14:36,559
(Yuci,)

257
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,559
(though I'm choosing to leave now,)

258
00:14:40,100 --> 00:14:41,990
(please don't ever think
it's because of you.)

259
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:48,679
(You didn't do anything wrong.)

260
00:14:50,519 --> 00:14:52,799
(You've been trying your best
to protect everyone.)

261
00:14:56,559 --> 00:14:58,000
(I'm the one who wasn't good enough.)

262
00:14:59,820 --> 00:15:00,639
Rao Yuci!

263
00:15:00,639 --> 00:15:02,080
(I just want you to believe)

264
00:15:05,020 --> 00:15:06,780
(that the reason
I approached you at first)

265
00:15:07,919 --> 00:15:09,399
(is that I've always remembered)

266
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:13,150
(the girl who held an umbrella for me)

267
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:16,559
(on a rainy night 15 years ago.)

268
00:15:26,799 --> 00:15:27,600
(Yuci,)

269
00:15:29,399 --> 00:15:30,600
(I wish you all the best.)

270
00:15:47,159 --> 00:15:48,200
(This house)

271
00:15:49,679 --> 00:15:51,440
(witnessed my journey of fighting back.)

272
00:15:53,159 --> 00:15:53,960
(Now,)

273
00:15:55,159 --> 00:15:56,600
(I'm finally leaving.)

274
00:15:58,639 --> 00:16:00,159
(If everything could start over,)

275
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:03,240
(I would choose to let all grievances)

276
00:16:03,679 --> 00:16:04,639
(fade away)

277
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:06,919
(and leave the hatred behind.)

278
00:16:07,380 --> 00:16:12,100
(Five years ago)

279
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:31,519
Not asleep yet?

280
