292
00:17:09,759 --> 00:17:11,799
Does this have to do with Liangliang?

293
00:17:13,279 --> 00:17:14,079
No.

294
00:17:17,559 --> 00:17:19,160
I just feel like

295
00:17:20,319 --> 00:17:21,640
