296
00:17:25,599 --> 00:17:27,119
People change.

297
00:17:27,839 --> 00:17:29,079
With the environment

298
00:17:29,079 --> 00:17:30,039
and circumstances,

299
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:32,000
