308
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:54,540
Aren't we besties? Have you forgotten?

309
00:18:12,559 --> 00:18:13,359
Yes.

310
00:18:24,279 --> 00:18:25,079
(Now,)

311
00:18:26,319 --> 00:18:27,599
