she was sentenced to three years.)

347
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:12,990
(For the crime of false accusation,
she was sentenced to three years.)

348
00:22:13,040 --> 00:22:15,029
(With multiple sentences combined,)

349
00:22:15,030 --> 00:22:20,020
