376
00:25:25,519 --> 00:25:27,799
Welcome to the Morning Information
Exchange Meeting.

377
00:25:27,799 --> 00:25:28,599
Don't be nervous.

378
00:25:28,680 --> 00:25:29,880
Just relax.

379
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:31,519
