438
00:27:50,359 --> 00:27:51,759
Can't you stop being so impulsive?

439
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:53,680
You have to believe in Rao Yuci.

440
00:27:54,480 --> 00:27:55,039
I think

441
00:27:55,039 --> 00:27:56,279
