443
00:27:59,759 --> 00:28:01,319
How could I not know her?

444
00:28:02,759 --> 00:28:04,480
She must be planning something big.

445
00:28:05,799 --> 00:28:06,759
Since I'm temporarily

446
00:28:06,759 --> 00:28:08,119
