451
00:28:37,799 --> 00:28:39,119
Who said I don't need you?

452
00:28:40,759 --> 00:28:42,599
It's just that your battlefield
isn't here.

453
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,480
Between us,

454
00:28:52,599 --> 00:28:53,920
I won't say I'm sorry.

455
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:00,800
You're useless at everything,

456
00:29:00,950 --> 00:29:02,039
