457
00:29:02,079 --> 00:29:02,880
Just drink up.

458
00:29:10,640 --> 00:29:11,440
Come on.

459
00:29:13,880 --> 00:29:15,359
Come on.

460
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:16,640
To the big idiot.

461
00:29:17,279 --> 00:29:18,279
To the big idiot.

