466
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:32,480
He must have drunk a lot.

467
00:29:33,119 --> 00:29:34,480
With Lysen in my hands,

468
00:29:35,799 --> 00:29:36,839
I hope it can be a company

469
00:29:36,839 --> 00:29:38,359
