472
00:29:42,680 --> 00:29:43,680
Because only in this way

473
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:44,839
can we create

474
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:46,759
true value for our investors

475
00:29:46,759 --> 00:29:47,759
and ourselves.

476
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:53,359
Lysen will open its arms

477
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:55,839
to welcome any form of cooperation.

478
00:29:56,119 --> 00:29:57,360
We will achieve win-win results

479
00:29:57,759 --> 00:29:59,880
and create our new glory.

480
00:30:03,039 --> 00:30:04,150
For the Lysen of the future,

481
00:30:06,240 --> 00:30:07,519
I hope it can still

482
00:30:07,519 --> 00:30:08,599
maintain a sense of awe.

483
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:10,640
Not just to

484
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:12,920
