487
00:30:16,630 --> 00:30:17,980
With an international perspective,

488
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:21,839
we will jointly maintain the country's
economic prosperity and stability.

489
00:30:22,119 --> 00:30:22,960
A new era,

490
00:30:23,720 --> 00:30:24,559
new people,

491
00:30:25,279 --> 00:30:26,079
new finance,

492
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:27,720
new hope.

493
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,000
To make this world

494
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:31,240
better and better,

495
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:33,440
work hard,

496
00:30:34,359 --> 00:30:35,160
work hard,

497
00:30:36,079 --> 00:30:36,880
work hard.

498
00:30:38,279 --> 00:30:39,079
Let's strive.

499
00:30:39,759 --> 00:30:40,599
Thank you.

500
00:30:49,079 --> 00:30:49,920
Tian Tian,

501
00:30:50,039 --> 00:30:51,880
the comrade Mr. Yu mentioned was...

502
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:53,880
She is a legend

503
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:54,839
at our Lysen.

504
00:31:11,240 --> 00:31:12,160
You can cry now.

505
00:31:15,759 --> 00:31:17,279
It's safe here. No one else is around.

506
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:19,440
Just me.

507
00:31:25,000 --> 00:31:26,290
Aren't you tired of following me?

508
00:31:29,359 --> 00:31:30,400
I told you,

509
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:33,000
after leaving the treatment center,

510
00:31:33,559 --> 00:31:35,119
