511
00:31:35,920 --> 00:31:36,920
Your family and friends

512
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:38,079
are not your enemies.

513
00:31:39,210 --> 00:31:41,480
Stepping out of that small world
of the Xinkang Treatment Center,

514
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:42,720
this is a new world.

515
00:31:42,839 --> 00:31:43,640
Rao Yuci,

516
00:31:44,390 --> 00:31:46,119
trying to let down
your guard around others

517
00:31:46,119 --> 00:31:47,319
is something you must do.

518
00:31:51,279 --> 00:31:53,270
It's impossible for everyone
around you to be bad.

519
00:31:54,720 --> 00:31:55,519
Trust me.

520
00:31:57,839 --> 00:31:58,680
(You seem to)

521
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:00,920
(need a long time)

522
00:32:00,920 --> 00:32:02,079
(to heal yourself.)

523
00:32:03,880 --> 00:32:05,440
(You need someone to try)

524
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:07,359
(standing in your shoes)

525
00:32:08,039 --> 00:32:09,519
(to feel everything you've endured.)

526
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:11,640
(They can't judge easily,)

527
00:32:12,480 --> 00:32:14,079
(nor can they jump to conclusions.)

528
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:16,759
(But)

529
00:32:18,519 --> 00:32:19,319
(I feel you have)

530
00:32:19,319 --> 00:32:20,640
(an amazing strength.)

531
00:32:22,559 --> 00:32:23,599
(And this strength)

532
00:32:24,799 --> 00:32:26,039
