540
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:41,720
(Rao Yuci, if you
need anything, just call me)

541
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:44,079
(It makes them unable
to pull away from you.)

542
00:32:45,680 --> 00:32:46,480
(They even)

543
00:32:47,839 --> 00:32:49,200
