544
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:52,680
(You seem to have a kind of magic)

545
00:32:54,160 --> 00:32:55,400
(that attracts others.)

546
00:32:57,039 --> 00:32:58,839
(Even if that magic is dangerous.)

547
00:32:59,319 --> 00:33:00,359
It will all pass.

548
00:33:01,319 --> 00:33:02,119
(I hope)

549
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:04,559
(you can take)

550
00:33:04,559 --> 00:33:05,640
(a good look at this world.)

551
00:33:07,090 --> 00:33:08,559
(There are many corners of the world)

552
00:33:08,559 --> 00:33:10,519
(that are not just
about self-serving interests.)

553
00:33:12,599 --> 00:33:13,960
(There are still many)

554
00:33:13,960 --> 00:33:15,160
(joyful things in this world.)

555
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:16,039
It's not as bad

556
00:33:16,039 --> 00:33:16,960
