557
00:33:16,960 --> 00:33:22,340
♪I wish I could
watch every view with you♪

558
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,000
If it's possible,

559
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:30,160
there's someone who can face
all of this with you

560
00:33:32,640 --> 00:33:33,799
and protect you,

561
00:33:34,160 --> 00:33:34,960
are...

562
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:39,359
