563
00:33:40,660 --> 00:33:47,660
♪Nothing more,
I need just to stay by your side♪

564
00:34:07,100 --> 00:34:14,020
♪Take a breath
and swallow the words you couldn't say♪

565
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:16,960
Hello, Rao Yuci.

566
00:34:21,119 --> 00:34:22,119
Hello, Chen Mo.

